summary: Walking Distance Of Shoreditch And Upper Street - This brand new boutique development of five stunning and spacious apartments has just come to market with Felicity J Lord. The development is located between vibrant Upper Street, Essex Road, Dalston, Broadway Market, Hoxton and Shoreditch.

A luxurious new two bedroom apartment offering 811 sq ft of living space. It will be completed to the highest specification including, colour video entry system, Neff and Bosch integrated appliances, fitted storage cupboards and many more.

Walking Distance Of Angel Station - Islington Square offers a selection of Dakota suites and one, two and three bedroom apartments across three buildings. These sit along with maisonettes and penthouses in one of London’s most sought after locations.

Studio Apartment - The conversion of this Edwardian Royal Mail sorting office into large warehouse apartments retains many of the original features including high ceilings and ornate detailing. Inside are very modern living spaces with unique floor plans

Modern Living - A new destination in the heart of vibrant Islington. Islington Square sits on the site of the former North London Royal Mail sorting and delivery centre. It will complement and extend the neighbourhood’s existing and thriving community.

Walking Distance Of Angel Station - Felicity J Lord are pleased to offer a completely original building by renowned architects CZWG designed as an eye-catching centrepiece to Islington Square. Contemporary, highly sustainable and destined to be one of the borough's most iconic buildings.
